metadata.name: Dakota in forest
metadata.description:
Dakota is a model with many years of experience in filming, with a beautiful appearance, artistry and charisma, we were able to create breathtaking shots. One of these shots, I was able to shoot in the forest using a Kiev 60 film camera to convey the smoothness and depth of the picture.

Camera: Kiev 60
Film: 6x6 Kodak Portra 160
Scan size: 3035x3035
